  "title": "ISic001362. Funerary inscription for Leontia and Kalliope",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ἐν\n                    θάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ἐν-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>θάδε</span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κῖτε</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Λε\n                    οντία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Λε\n                    οντία\"><span data-text=\"Λε\n                    οντία\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Λεοντία\">Λε-<br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>οντία</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἐτ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ῶ</span>(ν)</span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\"><span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"γ\">γ</span>´</span>  <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span><span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ἐνθάδε</span>  <span data-text=\"κῖ\n                    τε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κῖ-<br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>τε</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Καλλι\n                    όπη\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Καλλι\n                    όπη\"><span data-text=\"Καλλι\n                    όπη\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Καλλιόπη\">Καλλι-<br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>όπη</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἐτ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ῶ</span>(ν)</span>  <br id=\"al9-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>🕎 <span data-text=\"ιη\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ιη\">ιη</span>´ 🕎 etrog </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ἐνθάδε</span>  <span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κῖτε</span>  <span data-text=\"Λεοντία\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Λεοντία\">Λεοντία</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἐτῶν</span>  <span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"γ\">γ</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ἐνθάδε</span>  <span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κῖτε</span>  <span data-text=\"Καλλιόπη\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Καλλιόπη\">Καλλιόπη</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἐτῶν</span>  <span data-text=\"ιη\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ιη\">ιη</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ἐν\n                    θάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΘΑΔΕ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΙΤΕ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Λε\n                    οντία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Λε\n                    οντία\"><span data-text=\"Λε\n                    οντία\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Λεοντία\">ΛΕ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΟΝΤΙΑ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ω</span></span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\"><span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"γ\">Γ</span></span><br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span><span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"κῖ\n                    τε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΙ<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ΤΕ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Καλλι\n                    όπη\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Καλλι\n                    όπη\"><span data-text=\"Καλλι\n                    όπη\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Καλλιόπη\">ΚΑΛΛΙ<br id=\"al8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>ΟΠΗ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ω</span></span><br id=\"al9-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>🕎<span data-text=\"ιη\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ιη\">ΙΗ</span>🕎etrog</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΙΤΕ</span><span data-text=\"Λεοντία\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Λεοντία\">ΛΕΟΝΤΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"γ\">Γ</span><span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"κῖτε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΙΤΕ</span><span data-text=\"Καλλιόπη\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Καλλιόπη\">ΚΑΛΛΙΟΠΗ</span><span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"ιη\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ιη\">ΙΗ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001362_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; Photograph of front face by students of Liceo M.M. Lazzaro, 2017-04-27\" src=\"ISic001362_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001362.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; Photograph of front face by students of Liceo M.M. Lazzaro, 2017-04-27\" src=\"ISic001362-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><p>  <span>  <span>Text based on photographs</span>  </span>; <span>  <span>Torremuzza and Franz observed only the first epitaph, without the indication of the age</span>  </span>; <span class=\"9\">9: <span>The second menorah is followed by an ethrog (or a shofar according to Ferrara)</span>  </span>  </p></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Here lies Leontia, aged 3. Here lies Kalliope, aged 18.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">Serena Agodi</p>  <p>Qui giace Leontia di anni 3. Qui giace Calliope di anni 18.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>These two Jewish epitaphs may not come from Catania: in describing the Biscari collection, Ferrara gives an imprecise indication of the provenance of this inscription and the structure <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἔνθαδε κεῖται ὁ δεῖνα ἐτῶν</span> is rather typical of the inscriptions from the Monteverde catacombs and not attested elsewhere in Catania. On the provenance, see the discussion in Korhonen 2001: 90-93. In any case, a Jewish community is well attested in Catania, as IMusCatania 228 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000781\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000781</a> of the 4th cent. CE confirms. The two girls were probably related (perhaps sisters). Both names are attested in the Jewish environment: both Leontia, probably a Jewish translation of Judith attested in CIJ 369 (Rome), and Kalliope, attested in BS II 136, 137, 200 (Beth She’arim, see also the Christian inscriptions of Syracuse IGCVO 948, 1321), however, are also popular among non-Jews (on both names, see Rutgers 1997: 249-250).</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 51.1199 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 46.1243 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> 1(2).650 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001385\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001385</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1769 174 no.71 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1784 185 no.73 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</a>  </li><li> Ferrara 1829 351 no.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005</a>  </li><li> Kirchhoff 1877 9494 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">536</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Ferrua 1938 72 no.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002004\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002004</a>  </li><li> Wilson 1990 310-311 fig.264b <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001509</a>  </li><li> 1993 no.146 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000166\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000166</a>  </li><li> Gebbia 1996 68 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002240\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002240</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 364 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li> Rutgers 1997 248 no.29, 249-250 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001614\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001614</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2001 90-93 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001425\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001425</a>  </li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Letters with serifs: Α, Δ, Λ with extended serifs, Α with broken bar, lunate Ε, cursive Ω. The supraline indicates the abbreviation of ν. In the lower corner of the stone are two menorah and a conical figure, perhaps an ethrog (a type of citron, used in the festival of Sukkot) or an amphora. According to Ferrare, the symbol can represent a shofar (a small ram's-horn trumpet). Kaibel did not understand this symbol, interpreting it as part of a Υ.<p> Lines 1-9  11-21  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  </p></div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
